node.title: Man dies after water-related incident at Masterson school
node.description: A 58-year-old man has died following a water-related incident at a Masterton school earlier this week.
node.content:
["A 58-year-old man has died following a water-related incident at St Matthew's Collegiate School in Masterton on Monday.", "", "
St Matthew's Collegiate School in Masterton. Photo: Google Maps
", "In a statement today, police said the man died in Wellington Hospital.", "Police are making inquiries on behalf of the coroner, who will release their findings in due course."]
